snippet.title: Overstep - Early-Access Gameplay Trailer - FREE TO PLAY
snippet.description:
Overstep launched Steam Early-Access on the 22nd of November! 
Play FREE now! http://bit.ly/OverstepGame

Overstep is a fast-paced 3 versus 3  third-person shooter, that offers refreshing gameplay through acrobatic movement that’s combined with combat. Overstep is a free-to-play game with cosmetic in-app-purchases. 

• Score points for entertaining the crowd
• Acrobatic and stylish movement
• Multiplayer
• Arcade like gameplay experience
• Customize your robot to your liking

Follow Overstep on Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/overstepgame/
Follow Overstep on Twitter - https://twitter.com/overstepgame
Follow Overstep on Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/OverstepGame/?fref=ts
Join our community! - discord.gg/Overstep
Check out Overstep page - http://www.overstepgame.com/
